<h2>Overview:</h2>
<p>The Catalog team is performing an activity to import standard products from the catalog of certain brands like Taparia and SKF. Currently they are required to follow this process manually. To minimize their efforts, we propose a feature to bulk import products in the database</p>

<h2>Process</h2>
<ol>
  <li>
    <p>
    Click here to visit the Product list page as given below
    </p>
    <%= image_tag "trainings/multipe_products6.png", class: "training_img" %>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
    Click on the “Bulk Upload” button. You will be redirected to the following page
    </p>
    <%= image_tag "trainings/multipe_products2.png", class: "training_img" %>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
    Click on the “Download Excel Template” button. An Excel file will be downloaded to your computer. The excel file will be as given below. 
    </p>
    <%= image_tag "trainings/multipe_products1.png", class: "training_img" %>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
    Enter the data in the template.
    </p>
    <%= image_tag "trainings/multipe_products8.png", class: "training_img" %>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
    Click on save and close the template file. Open Sprint to upload the saved file.
    </p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
    Upload the template file and click on the “Create Product Import” button
    </p>
    <%= image_tag "trainings/multipe_products4.png", class: "training_img" %>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
    The process will run at that background. Once the upload is complete, you will receive an email notification as given below.
