    <%= image_tag "trainings/multipe_products5.png", class: "training_img" %>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
    The email attachment will have an error report file to highlight the unsuccessful upload results along with the error message. The report will look like this. 
    </p>
    <%= image_tag "trainings/multipe_products7.png", class: "training_img" %>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>
    The email attachment will have an error report file to highlight the unsuccessful upload results along with the error message. The report will look like this. 
    </p>
  </li>
</ol>
<h2>Pre-requisites</h2>
<ol>
  <li>The users must enter all the mandatory fields.</li>
  <li>The user must enter correct data in the required format</li>
  <li>The brand name must exist in the database before the upload.</li>
  <li>The active category_id must be entered in the given field (category_id can be found on this page)</li>
  <li>The tax Code has to be correct and must exist in the sprint database before the upload. In case of invalid tax code, the system will skip the row and that particular product will not be uploaded.</li>
</ol>
